From edd at debian.org  Wed May 29 01:49:59 2013
From: edd at debian.org (Dirk Eddelbuettel)
Date: Tue, 28 May 2013 18:49:59 -0500
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] How to access fields and methods of a RefClass
	from	C++?
